Site about Pizza Restaurant La Regina. It is build form scratch with HTML, CSS and JavaScript Code. The site contains many pages(Home, Menu, Ordering page, About us page) with different functions. Different products 
can be ordered from "Make an order" page, and when the order is placed, a form appears for filling in the user's information. The fields for information are protected.
After placing an order, a message appears from the browser with general information about the order.
